{
  "texts": [
    "One method is to introduce self-learning knowledge management systems that utilize AI techniques such as natural language processing, text clustering, and classification rule learning to enable continuous improvement and expansion of the knowledge base.",
    "Regular checks and updates can ensure that the information remains current and relevant.",
    "Furthermore, incorporating collaborative filtering and user feedback mechanisms can help identify and fill gaps in the knowledge base, making sure that the AI system has access to comprehensive and accurate data.",
    "Using AI in customer service brings up important ethical and transparency concerns.",
    "Customers are worried about how their data is being used, the fairness of AI decision-making, and overall transparency of AI operations."
  ]
}